%define         uversion 2021-01-28
Name:           openkim-models
Version:        2021.01.28
Release:        0
Summary:        Open Knowledgebase of Interatomic Models
License:        CDDL-1.0 AND Apache-2.0 AND MPL-2.0 AND GPL-3.0-only AND LGPL-3.0-only
Group:          Productivity/Scientific/Chemistry
